## `<file-level: FUSE submodule public API>`
<!-- checksum: rust-fuse-mod-1 -->

### Purpose
Public surface for the optional FUSE adapter. The entire submodule is gated behind `#[cfg(feature = "fuse")]` in `lib.rs`, so a library consumer who doesn't enable the feature never sees `fuser` in their dep tree.

### Implementation Notes

```rust
pub mod adapter;

pub use adapter::{mount, Adapter, MountOptions};
```

